{"tid":228450,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"只能夠平平淡淡咁過普通既生活","createTime":"2017-05-04T01:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T04:04:57.000Z","uid":76855,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5585d7884654b62bb40704569893722e0a9ecaa0","tid":228450,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"hi<br />\n<br />\n我今年22歲 a1<br />\n<br />\n住層爛鬼私樓，得500呎<br />\n<br />\n今年就要畢業了<br />\n<br />\n我讀既係BU bba<br />\n<br />\nyr2個時夢想係入外資銀行，成為金融財俊，做個高級中產<br />\n<br />\nsummer break時搵intern，發現原來身邊啲同學都有uncle照<br />\n<br />\nFinance major個mk仔，上lecture成日9up串到死，因為識人所以去左番ifc<br />\n<br />\n我gpa 3.5 就去左中銀做個intern仔，得$5000 一個月<br />\n<br />\n到yr3個時，老母又衰貪心，炒股輸左成二百幾萬<br />\n<br />\n搞到個時老豆賣撚左架車，我就番高級餐廳幫補家計<br />\n<br />\n個年之後CGPA跌到落2.9，咩大公司基本上都冇我份<br />\n<br />\n屋企又冇錢供我讀Master<br />\n<br />\nsend左好多CV出去都係得啲本地細行出13k<br />\n<br />\n呢4年又冇錢去外國exchange，得閒就淨係番啲無聊工搵$60個鐘，基本上冇develop過自己<br />\n<br />\n唉，當日仲以為自己好特別，會出人頭地，入大行，搵大錢<br />\n<br />\n點知原來好多機會都唔到我擁有<br />\n<br />\n同好多香港人一樣，只能夠平平淡淡咁過普通既生活<br />\n<br />\n聽日就考final了，希望一切順利吧。"},{"pid":"9ded5b909e41f6e7d66e36dcb01bc8c3141701f1","tid":228450,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b54623410de323dd9a046fb033acf987e06b464","tid":228450,"uid":33070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d09b3fb416b763067a4b802809ff17eb0ca9f9af","tid":228450,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef3c09daf208842cbd6c1359098a20fd9dd82b51","tid":228450,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5060202337c454cd37b2726acb6021dfa931e2c","tid":228450,"ui